    "name": "WorkForcePro API Collection",
    "description": "API test collection for WorkForcePro Employee Training Management System.\n\nObjective  \nAPI test collection created for the WorkForcePro QA Assignment.\n\nAssumptions:\n\n- No actual API server provided.\n    \n- Endpoints are created based on assignment requirements.\n    \n- Request and response schemas are assumed.\n    \n\n**Covered Scenarios**\n\nEmployee API  \n\\- Create Employee  \n\\- Get Employee  \n\\- Duplicate Email Validation  \n\\- Missing Employee ID Validation  \n\\- Update Employee  \n\\- Delete Employee\n\nTraining API  \n_- Assign Training  \n\\- Complete Training  \n\\- Approve Training  \n\\- Invalid Training ID  \n\\- Approve Non-Completed Training  \n\\- Complete Unassigned Training\n\nBusiness Rules Validated  \n\\- Employee must have a unique email.  \n\\- Employee ID is mandatory.  \n\\- Training must be assigned before completion.  \n\\- Training must be completed before approval.  \n\\- Invalid training IDs are rejected.  \n\\- Appropriate success and error status codes are returned.  \n\\- API response time validation included where applicable.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "56172758",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/56172758-493ce2fa-d462-4dc2-9f0b-ba0018a8d3f9?source=collection_link"
  },
  
